{"id": "18211", "post": "<div class=\"post-18211 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers\" id=\"post-18211\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/giveaway-follow-lowendbox-on-facebook-twitter-to-win-free-vps-hybrid-servers-shared-reseller-hosting-more/\" rel=\"bookmark\">[GIVEAWAY] Follow LowEndBox on Facebook &amp; Twitter to win free VPS, hybrid servers, shared/reseller hosting &amp; more!</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> December 17, 2018 @ 8:00 pm, by Daniel Spritzer</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p></p><center><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/LEBHolidayBanner.jpg.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18214 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/LEBHolidayBanner.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"400\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></center><p></p><div></div><div>LowEndBox is committed to continuing to be a resourceful tool for you to find and locate all things hosting. We want to be the go to site you reference to any time you need a hosting solution \u2013 whether it\u2019s shared hosting, reseller hosting, VPS, dedicated servers \u2013 or anything else in between. What originally started off as a personal hobby has now grew into a platform to help others achieve affordable hosting, and we are sincerely grateful for all of your support into the community throughout the years. We are proud to say the LEB spirit is still alive and strong \u2013 thanks to you!</div><div></div><p></p><div>That being said, we have some exciting news in the pipeline and would like to grow our social media following, as well as host a giveaway in spirit of the holidays. We\u2019ve contacted several different hosts to see who would be interested in sponsoring a giveaway to help make this more eventful.</div><div></div><div><p>So in exchange for following us on Twitter&nbsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lowendnetwork\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@LowEndNetwork</a>&nbsp;and/or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lowendofficial/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><wbr>Facebook</a>, you will be entered in a raffle to win one of the following gifts<b>&nbsp;(WOW, total of 30 freebies will be given away!)</b></p></div><div><div><b>Here\u2019s what we will be raffling away:</b></div><p></p><div></div><div><b>\u2013 5x Free 1 GB RAM OVZ VPS for life sponsored by&nbsp;</b><a href=\"https://www.umaxhosting.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">UMaxHosting</a></div><div><b>\u2013 2x $100 Account Credit&nbsp;sponsored by&nbsp;</b><a href=\"https://www.hudsonvalleyhost.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HudsonValleyHost</a></div><div><b>\u2013 2x Free 100GB Reseller Hosting account for one year sponsored by&nbsp;</b><a href=\"https://www.megazonehosting.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MegaZoneHosting</a></div><div><b>\u2013 2x 3 months free on a&nbsp;2GB Linux KVM VPS from&nbsp;</b><a href=\"https://www.chicagovps.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ChicagoVPS</a></div><div><b>\u2013 1x 6 months free on a 8GB SSD KVM VPS sponsored by&nbsp;</b><a href=\"https://www.hostbrz.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HostBRZ</a></div><div><b>\u2013 5x 200GB Shared Hosting accounts free for 3 years sponsored by&nbsp;</b><a href=\"https://www.solvedbydata.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SolvedByData</a></div><div><b>\u2013 5x 768MB SSD OVZ VPS free for life, sponsored by&nbsp;</b><a href=\"https://www.supremevps.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SupremeVPS</a></div><div><b>\u2013 5x $25 Account Credit sponsored by&nbsp;</b><a href=\"https://www.n3servers.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">n3Servers</a><p></p><div>The winners will be randomly chosen as well as the freebie. The winners will be announced on Jan 4, 2019 to kick off the New Year with a BLAST!</div><div></div><p></p><div>After following us on a social media channel (Twitter or Facebook), you&nbsp;<b>MUST</b>&nbsp;comment on this post saying something along the lines of \u201cdone\u201d or \u201ccount me in\u201d in order to be eligible to be apart of the raffle, as we will be randomly selecting the winners from the comments section below and contacting you via e-mail if you do win!</div><div></div><p></p><div>Good luck and please let us know if you have any questions/comments!</div></div></div><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fgiveaway-follow-lowendbox-on-facebook-twitter-to-win-free-vps-hybrid-servers-shared-reseller-hosting-more%2F&amp;t=%5BGIVEAWAY%5D%20Follow%20LowEndBox%20on%20Facebook%20%26%20Twitter%20to%20win%20free%20VPS%2C%20hybrid%20servers%2C%20shared%2Freseller%20hosting%20%26%20more%21\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=%5BGIVEAWAY%5D%20Follow%20LowEndBox%20on%20Facebook%20%26%20Twitter%20to%20win%20free%20VPS%2C%20hybrid%20servers%2C%20shared%2Freseller%20hosting%20%26%20more%21&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fgiveaway-follow-lowendbox-on-facebook-twitter-to-w